### 6. 通用 HTTP 客户端

任何支持 HTTP 的客户端都可以直接调用：

```bash
# 获取工具列表
curl http://localhost:8101/mcp

# 调用工具

curl -X POST http://localhost:8101/mcp?sessionId=test \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $(cat ~/electron-mcp-token.txt)" \
  -d '{
  "method": "tools/list",
  "params": {
  },
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 0
}'

# 使用认证令牌
curl -X POST http://localhost:8101/mcp?sessionId=test \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $(cat ~/electron-mcp-token.txt)" \
  -d '{
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_windows",
    "arguments": {}
  },
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 5
}'

# MCP 端点
curl http://localhost:8101/mcp
```

